This topic contains release notes for ClamAV Add-on for PCF v1.3.
## v1.3.28 (GA)

**Release Date:** January 24, 2018

This release of ClamAV Add-on for PCF:

* Includes an updated open source license disclosure file.
* Acceptance tests for Windows have been updated for the BOSH CLI v2.

## v1.3.11 (GA)

**Release Date:** November 22, 2017

This release of ClamAV Add-on for PCF:

* Includes a new feature for retry when running freshclam
* Scheduled scans can be configured to be daily or hourly
* Start times for schedule scans are pseudorandom so that not all VMs in the deployment start at the same time


## v1.3.7 (GA)

**Release Date:** September 29, 2017

This release of ClamAV Add-on for PCF:

* Adds support for Windows.
* Disables ScanHTML when On-Access and Scheduled Scans are enabled.

